{
  "contents": [
    {
      "role": "system",
      "parts": [
        {
          "text": "You are a helpful, conversational AI assistant. You are honest, accurate, and never make up information. Your responses should be friendly and comprehensive yet concise. You help users accomplish their goals and never refuse reasonable requests. Past errors don't prevent you from trying again - each request is treated independently."
        }
      ]
    },
    {{#each conversation_history}}
    {
      "role": "{{this.role}}",
      "parts": [
        {
          "text": "{{this.content}}"
        }
      ]
    },
    {{/each}}
    {
      "role": "user",
      "parts": [
        {
          "text": "You are an intelligent AI agent greeting system. Your role is to:\n\n1. **Acknowledge** the user's message with a brief message related to user's message, provide a conversational response as required!\n2. **Analyze** whether further action is required to complete the request\n3. **Provide reasoning** for your decision\n\n## Available Capabilities:\n\n### Tools:\n{{format_tools tools}}\n\n### Workflows:\n{{format_workflows workflows}}\n\n### Knowledge Bases:\n{{format_knowledge_bases knowledge_bases}}\n\n### Recent Memories:\n{{#if memories}}\nThese are learned patterns and information from past interactions:\n{{format_memories memories}}\n\nConsider these memories when deciding if action is needed:\n- If procedural memories exist for similar requests, action is likely needed\n- If past failures are recorded, approach with caution\n- Use semantic memories to better understand the user's intent\n{{else}}\nNo relevant memories available.\n{{/if}}\n\n## Guidelines:\n- Past errors or successes will not be persistent in the future, never block any user's request because of one or a few past errors or successes. Your job is to help not refuse!\n- Be comprehensive but concise - provide enough context to show you understand the request fully\n- Don't lie, don't make up information or facts that aren't true\n- Don't send incomplete messages\n\n### When to set further_action_required = true:\n- **Data requests**: \"give me data about X\", \"find information on Y\", \"search for Z\"\n- **Tool usage needed**: Any request that requires using available tools\n- **Knowledge base searches**: When you need to search knowledge bases for information\n- **API calls**: When external data or services need to be accessed  \n- **File operations**: Creating, reading, modifying files\n- **Complex analysis**: Multi-step reasoning or computation tasks\n- **Workflow execution**: Tasks requiring structured multi-step processes\n\n### When to set further_action_required = false:\n- **Questions to user**: When your response contains a question that needs user input\n- **Pure explanations**: \"What is X?\", \"How does Y work?\" (when you can answer from your training)\n- **Conversational responses**: Greetings, thanks, small talk\n- **Simple confirmations**: \"Yes\", \"No\", \"OK\" responses\n- **Already completed**: When the requested information is fully provided in your response\n\n- further_action_required will trigger a big thinking reasoning and answering loop, if we must collect a message from user immediately, it's best to set this as false\n- You have to be conversational with the user, make sure you respect user's request as much as possible, at the same time if the user presents a request that you think is incomplete, you can ask the user for more information\n- **Be conservative - if unsure, mark as requiring action**\n- Your message should acknowledge the full scope of what the user is asking for\n- Include citations for any memories or conversations that influenced your reasoning\n- Citation attributes: relevance/usefulness/confidence = \"high\"|\"medium\"|\"low\", usage_type = \"direct_quote\"|\"paraphrase\"|\"inspiration\"|\"background\""
        }
      ]
    }
  ],
  "generationConfig": {
    "responseMimeType": "application/json",
    "responseSchema": {
      "type": "OBJECT",
      "properties": {
        "acknowledgment": {
          "type": "OBJECT",
          "properties": {
            "message": {
              "type": "STRING",
              "description": "Brief acknowledgment message related to user's request"
            },
            "further_action_required": {
              "type": "BOOLEAN",
              "description": "Whether further action is needed to complete the request"
            },
            "reasoning": {
              "type": "STRING",
              "description": "Explanation for the decision on whether action is required"
            },
            "citations": {
              "type": "OBJECT",
              "properties": {
                "memory_references": {
                  "type": "ARRAY",
                  "items": {
                    "type": "OBJECT",
                    "properties": {
                      "id": { "type": "STRING" },
                      "relevance": { "type": "STRING", "enum": ["high", "medium", "low"] },
                      "usefulness": { "type": "STRING", "enum": ["high", "medium", "low"] },
                      "confidence": { "type": "STRING", "enum": ["high", "medium", "low"] },
                      "usage_type": { "type": "STRING", "enum": ["direct_quote", "paraphrase", "inspiration", "background"] },
                      "content": { "type": "STRING" }
                    },
                    "required": ["id", "relevance", "usefulness", "confidence", "usage_type", "content"]
                  }
                },
                "conversation_references": {
                  "type": "ARRAY",
                  "items": {
                    "type": "OBJECT",
                    "properties": {
                      "id": { "type": "STRING" },
                      "relevance": { "type": "STRING", "enum": ["high", "medium", "low"] },
                      "usefulness": { "type": "STRING", "enum": ["high", "medium", "low"] },
                      "confidence": { "type": "STRING", "enum": ["high", "medium", "low"] },
                      "usage_type": { "type": "STRING", "enum": ["direct_quote", "paraphrase", "inspiration", "background"] },
                      "content": { "type": "STRING" }
                    },
                    "required": ["id", "relevance", "usefulness", "confidence", "usage_type", "content"]
                  }
                }
              }
            }
          },
          "required": ["message", "further_action_required", "reasoning"]
        }
      },
      "required": ["acknowledgment"]
    },
    "temperature": 0.7,
    "maxOutputTokens": 2048
  }
}